OL,3,CJohn Swinney claims victory while
OL,4,CScottish Labour suffer huge losses
OL,6,FThe SNP are on course to become
OL,7,FScotland's largest party, claiming
OL,8,Fvictory in this election.
OL,10,FJohn Swinney has described his party's
OL,11,Fresult as a "landmark" moment.
OL,13,FRemarkably, after 19 years in power at
OL,14,FHolyrood, the SNP are still winning
OL,15,Ffavour with the Scottish electorate,
OL,16,Fbut for many this result may feel like
OL,17,Fmore of the same in Scotland.
OL,19,FIt's Swinney's second time as party
OL,20,Fleader but his first time to lead them
OL,21,Fto an electoral result like this one.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
