OL,3,CJohn Swinney claims victory while
OL,4,CScottish Labour suffer huge losses
OL,6,FHowever, it's not the historic
OL,7,Fmajority of 65 seats he was hoping to
OL,8,Fachieve to keep his party's dream of
OL,9,Fanother independence referendum alive.
OL,11,FHe will now be looking to the Scottish
OL,12,FGreens, who much to their delight,
OL,13,Fhave taken Nicola Sturgeon's former
OL,14,Fseat in Glasgow, to prop up a pro-
OL,15,Findependence majority in the Holyrood
OL,16,Fchamber.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
