OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778328667
OL,3,CJohn Swinney claims victory while
OL,4,CScottish Labour suffer huge losses
OL,6,FThe party have won their first ever
OL,7,Fconstituency seats while also
OL,8,Foverthrowing an SNP titan in
OL,9,FEdinburgh. Angus Robertson, a former
OL,10,Fsenior minister in the SNP and deputy
OL,11,Fparty leader, was ousted.
OL,13,FElsewhere, Scottish Labour have had a
OL,14,Fdisastrous result so far in this
OL,15,Felection.
OL,17,FTheir leader Anas Sarwar lost his
OL,18,Fconstituency seat in Glasgow,
OL,19,Fadmitting they lost the argument for
OL,20,Fchange. He's made it through on the
OL,21,Fregional list vote to remain an MSP.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
