CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778328667
OL,3,CJohn Swinney claims victory while
OL,4,CScottish Labour suffer huge losses
OL,6,FUndoubtedly there will be some soul
OL,7,Fsearching at Labour HQ.
OL,9,FSarwar and Secretary of State for
OL,10,FScotland Douglas Alexander led the
OL,11,Fcharge and will have to answer for its
OL,12,Ffailure.
OL,14,FSarwar tried to publicly distance
OL,15,Fhimself from Keir Starmer at the start
OL,16,Fof this campaign but it's clear now
OL,17,Fthat wasn't enough to convince the
OL,18,Felectorate in Scotland that he was the
OL,19,Fman for the job of First Minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
