OL,3,CJohn Swinney claims victory while
OL,4,CScottish Labour suffer huge losses
OL,6,FFor now, he has refused to be drawn on
OL,7,Fwhether he will stand down as party
OL,8,Fleader.
OL,10,FReform have split the unionist vote
OL,11,Fwith some arguing they've helped the
OL,12,FSNP.
OL,14,FTheir leader in Scotland, Malcolm
OL,15,FOfford, has been elected on the list
OL,16,Fvote for West of Scotland.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
