OL,3,CJohn Swinney claims victory while
OL,4,CScottish Labour suffer huge losses
OL,6,FMany of their MSPs are entering the
OL,7,Fworld of politics for the first time
OL,8,Fand they will certainly liven up the
OL,9,Fcorridors of Holyrood.
OL,11,FOfford joins two other party leaders
OL,12,Fto pick up seats from the list vote.
OL,14,FThe Scottish Greens co-leader Ross
OL,15,FGreer and Scottish Conservatives
OL,16,Fleader Russell Findlay will return as
OL,17,FMSPs to Holyrood.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
